the highest-quality spectra of the SDSS EDR, we show that this\nmodel can reproduce simultaneously the observed strengths of those Lick indices\nthat do not depend strongly on element abundance ratios [abridged].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Sep 2003 11:49:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
