 strong evidence for the\nexistence of a quark-gluon plasma in Au+Au collisions at RHIC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Sep 2003 17:07:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Sep 2003 12:38:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
